<Verse cite="John 14:3">And if I go and prepare a place for you, I will come back and take you to be with me that you also may be where I am.</Verse>

**The [Father](/vault/lexicon/father)'s house is open. The Son has cleared the way. Come home. And once you are home, leave the light on for someone else.**

